  <brief_title>Single Port Access (SPA) Cholecystectomy Versus Standard Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Port Access Cholecystectomy Versus Standard Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy - Randomized Study</official_title>
